  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "マイケル・ナイトは使命を持った男です。顔を撃たれた後、言わば生まれ変わったナイトは、正義のために人生を捧げることを決意します。自ら成功を収めた億万長者ウィルトン・ナイトは、ナイト財団の公共正義組織の主任フィールドエージェントとしてマイケルを雇います。この組織の一環として、KITT（ナイト・インダストリーズ・トゥーサウザンド）という超能力を持つ知能を備えたポンティアック・トランザムの開発が含まれています。KITTは時速300マイルで走行でき、防弾性や耐火性を持ち、会話もでき、マイケルが世界の不正と戦う手助けをします。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "A combat racing game featuring KITT and Michael Knight from the TV show Knight Rider. It was released exclusively in Japan for the PC Engine.\n\nKnight Rider Special is a driving game with vehicular combat that was released for the PC Engine in 1989. It is based on the 1980s TV show Knight Rider, about the secret agent Michael Knight and the Knight Industries Two Thousand (KITT) technologically-enhanced vehicle with its own sophisticated AI. The game employs the memorable music from the TV show and also features the Japanese voice actor for KITT, who lends his voice to a few soundbites.\n\nThe goal of the game is to race to the end of each stage, avoiding other vehicles on the road and employing KITT's turbo boosters to make time, and then taking out the criminal Michael was sent to chase down with KITT's weaponry.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
